MAPPING.NAME: m_OPEN_ORDERS

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on REFERENCE table for getting division_desc
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_REFERENCE_PROFIT

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT Reference.Desc_1 as Desc_1, UPPER(Reference.Reference_sub_key_2) as Reference_sub_key_2 FROM Reference with (nolock) WHERE Reference.Reference_key='HAAProfitMapping'

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT MIN(SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_ID) as FACILITY_ID, SLBA_FACILITY.DIVISION_GROUP as DIVISION_GROUP FROM SLBA_FACILITY WHERE SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_CODE IN ($$FACILITY_CODE) GROUP BY SLBA_FACILITY.DIVISION_GROUP

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on SLBA_ITEM for division group hbi
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_SLBA_ITEM_HBI

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT MIN(SLBA_ITEM.ITEM_ID) as ITEM_ID, SLBA_ITEM.DIVISION_GROUP as DIVISION_GROUP FROM SLBA_ITEM WHERE SLBA_ITEM.STYLE_NUM in ($$STYLE_NUM) GROUP BY SLBA_ITEM.DIVISION_GROUP

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on SLBA_ITEM for getting DIV_DESC
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_SLBA_ITEM_DIV

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT Reference.Desc_1 as Desc_1, Reference.Reference_key as Reference_key, Reference.Reference_subkey_seq as Reference_subkey_seq FROM Reference with (nolock)

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT MIN(SLBA_ITEM.ITEM_ID) as ITEM_ID, SLBA_ITEM.SKU as SKU, SLBA_ITEM.DIVISION_GROUP as DIVISION_GROUP FROM SLBA_ITEM GROUP BY SLBA_ITEM.SKU, SLBA_ITEM.DIVISION_GROUP

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT MIN(SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_ID) as FACILITY_ID, SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_CODE as FACILITY_CODE, SLBA_FACILITY.DIVISION_GROUP as DIVISION_GROUP FROM SLBA_FACILITY GROUP BY SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_CODE, SLBA_FACILITY.DIVISION_GROUP

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Source qualifier to read from STG_HAA_OPEN_ORDERS
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_STG_HAA_OPEN_ORDERS

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT STG_HAA_OPEN_ORDERS.COMPANY_CODE, STG_HAA_OPEN_ORDERS.SKU, STG_HAA_OPEN_ORDERS.ACCOUNT_NUMBER, STG_HAA_OPEN_ORDERS.STORE_NUMBER, STG_HAA_OPEN_ORDERS.ORDER_NUMBER, STG_HAA_OPEN_ORDERS.ORDER_SUFFIX, STG_HAA_OPEN_ORDERS.ORDERED_DATE, STG_HAA_OPEN_ORDERS.REQUESTED_SHIP_DATE, STG_HAA_OPEN_ORDERS.CANCEL_BY_DATE, STG_HAA_OPEN_ORDERS.CUST_PURCHASE_ORDER_DT, STG_HAA_OPEN_ORDERS.RELEASE_CODE, STG_HAA_OPEN_ORDERS.RELEASED_DATE, STG_HAA_OPEN_ORDERS.CUST_PURCHASE_ORDNUM, STG_HAA_OPEN_ORDERS.OPEN_UNITS, STG_HAA_OPEN_ORDERS.OPEN_DOLLARS, STG_HAA_OPEN_ORDERS.ALLOCATED_UNITS, STG_HAA_OPEN_ORDERS.ALLOCATED_DOLLARS, STG_HAA_OPEN_ORDERS.EXTENDED_COST_DOLLARS, STG_HAA_OPEN_ORDERS.QUALITY_CODE, STG_HAA_OPEN_ORDERS.SHIP_FROM_FACILITYID, STG_HAA_OPEN_ORDERS.CREDIT_HOLD_CODE, STG_HAA_OPEN_ORDERS.BACKORDER_CODE, STG_HAA_OPEN_ORDERS.EVENT_CODE, STG_HAA_OPEN_ORDERS.PURCHASE_ORDER_TYPE, STG_HAA_OPEN_ORDERS.ORDER_TYPE, STG_HAA_OPEN_ORDERS.FINANCIAL_CLASS_CODE, STG_HAA_OPEN_ORDERS.OPEN_ORDER_UNITS, STG_HAA_OPEN_ORDERS.OPEN_ORDER_DOLLARS, STG_HAA_OPEN_ORDERS.RELEASED_ORDER_UNITS, STG_HAA_OPEN_ORDERS.RELEASED_ORDER_DOLLARS, STG_HAA_OPEN_ORDERS.CURRENCY_CODE FROM STG_HAA_OPEN_ORDERS ORDER BY STG_HAA_OPEN_ORDERS.ORDER_NUMBER
